{"tid":1720343,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"周梓樂手足頭七","createTime":"2019-11-14T10:21:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T04:55:51.000Z","uid":307619,"like":99,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"e7538808ad4a65f8ccbbeacea116310fdac79894","tid":1720343,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T10:21:12.000Z","msg":"#Nov14 #全港 #悼念周同學 <br />\n全港悼念周同學 ( 頭七 )<br />\n日期 : 11月14日 ( 四 )<br />\n時間 : 20 : 09<br />\n地點 : 任何地方<br />\n無論身處何地 請為周同學默哀一分鐘<br />\n<br />\n一個熱門post都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cc4bXeu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcc4bXeu.jpg&h=512b179b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/42W51Jg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F42W51Jg.jpg&h=879cbaf3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lm8j59X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLm8j59X.jpg&h=5df831e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c08e85a25a375bbe75440eddcd22da556ffbf42","tid":1720343,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T10:21:59.000Z","msg":"一陣大球場會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8708906702564bc70400f7ad9f360937a589e140","tid":1720343,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T10:23:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">中文大學醫學院矯形外科及創傷學系骨腫瘤科組教授古明達表示，周梓樂很大可能墮樓前已失知覺，墮地時不能保護自己，右邊盆骨先落地及產生強</span>大側邊撞擊力；一般有意識的人，從高處墮地時會自然反應，以手或捲曲身體保護自己，很大機會手腳有骨折。<br />\n<br />\n#周梓樂離世<br />\n【傷勢曝光！右髂骨折手腳無明顯傷患 創傷科專家：或墮樓前已失知覺】<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2pWhlRE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2pWhlRE&d=kXTsEwo%2F%2B0BMNdh3S%2FGVc%2FsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=e1225d31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2pWhlRE</a><br />\n【母校校長教師促獨立查死因】<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2X7EIDY\" data-sr-url=\"https: